data.description: 3411 W 151st in Cleveland's West Park neighborhood is a wonderful home. The property features three bedrooms, which is perfect for families or those who need extra space. The light and airy kitchen is a great feature, providing a bright and welcoming space for cooking and entertaining. The hardwood floors add a touch of elegance and durability to the home. The full basement provides additional storage and/or living space. The covered patio is a great feature for outdoor entertaining or relaxation in all types of weather. The well-landscaped yard is another great feature, providing a beautiful and peaceful outdoor space. The one-car garage is a convenient feature for parking and storage. Overall, this property is a fantastic place to call your home today.
